public class CmmnHandlerContext extends Object implements HandlerContext

This context contains necessary information (like caseDefinition) to be accessed by a CmmnHandlerContext.

      public CmmnActivity getParent()
      Description copied from interface: HandlerContext

      This method returns an activity. The returned activity represents a parent activity, which can contain activities.

      The returned activity should be used as a parent activity for a new activity.
